Product_description: It goes without saying that this set of 3 accent tiles is specifically designed for the child who is an ardent admirer of the Avengers superheroes. Our accent tiles are imprinted with chemical-free inks for a heroic and yet safe transformation of your child’s room décor.

Our Accent Tiles are printed with green UV inks on coated Ceramic tiles in size 8″ square. They have a tough velvet+rubber backing to avoid breakage or cracks. They are ready to hang with pre-installed brass hooks .

This set of accent tiles is a thing of beauty. Designed to represent the cosmic journeys that we go through every day, in the form of mornings, noon and nights, these tiles can transform a living space corner to a space studio. The eternal appeal of the sun, moon and stars adds to the intricate designs and colours, imprinted with green, chemical-free inks.
